body:
@dafrista I've done with my review: mostly adding comments. I'm happy to see the proto code that's stemmed from the old design is going away!
One thing to check. I'm not sure we have CI setup for .NET. We probably want to check this change does not break .NET part.

It'd be great to have a protocol diagram that shows interactions between components with messages (POJOs, proto or avro messages).
